textContent:
2.25 oz or 67.5 ml Gin
0.75 oz or 22.5 ml Aperol
2 Slices of cucumber

Gently muddle cucumber in mixing glass
Add ingredients and stir with ice
Strain over ice in rocks glass
Garnish with cucumber ribbon
